This folder contains a spider that will scrape data from 58同城
------------------Enviornment Setting-------------------------
need to pre-install scrapy

-----------------How to Install-------------------------------
install with homebrew or anaconda 
For other methods, please follow the specific instruction online

-----------------How to run-----------------------------------
type scrapy crawl eight -o [filename].csv

----------------How to resolve the coding---------------------
open excel first, and then choose import csv file
REMEMBER to CHANGE the coding option to UTF-8

-----------------How to Change the City Option----------------
For specific instructions, please read the comments in 
eight_spider.py
